</td></tr>
<tr class="sortbottom">
<td colspan="3" style="text-align:left;">
<p><small>Published in June 2012.<sup id="cite_ref-212" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-212">[195]</a></sup><br /> Survey conducted in February – March 2012.<br />
